506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T23:34:29.000Z","msg":"其實我都有諗過呢個問題。<br />\n話識別陽光個啲 咁北歐人點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 偏偏佢地壽命就好長 in average。<br />\n當然除左下訓教 都仲有好多唔同因素嘅"},{"pid":"fbe2f4464f7b04802e1def8a05cf5747dd8575e3","tid":517322,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T23:41:26.000Z","msg":"其實如果你食野都shift埋應該ok？<br />\n<br />\n例如11點食晚飯，2、3訓，訓到朝早10、11點食早餐，下午3、4點食晏<br />\n<br />\n個問題係咁混亂食飯時間夾唔到個社會，除非唔駛返工+自己煑"},{"pid":"4c36a39063845ed082e3635f36514df66b90c713","tid":517322,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673be790a274d0ec6462171e15d5e43f046c002f","tid":517322,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:07:23.000Z","msg":"你高或者成咗年夜訓就冇乜所謂，<br />\n矮仔未成年就建議就啲訓喇，<br />\n生長激素剩喺12點你訓咗先會分泌多啲"},{"pid":"17846816b90c799ebb45b2a703114e10f45783ae","tid":517322,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:19:08.000Z","msg":"你個身體習慣左咁多年<br />\n你覺得你個規律要幾耐先令身體適應到？"},{"pid":"ee60fd003ebf51b67cfc8b476beba1c3adcce1c3","tid":517322,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"80f408bf95e141b8bebefe691e489a3dc129d8a3","tid":517322,"uid":28181,"like":7,"dislike":27,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"8ce7f89688ae9481c39c0287ebc87274dd20a297","tid":517322,"uid":133865,"like":173,"dislike":2,"score":171,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T07:52:57.000Z","msg":"黑夜會產生退黑色素，會增加睡眠質素<br />\n當然如果你可以喺朝早制造到一個同夜晚一樣黑既環境，就應該冇問題"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T17:43:12.000Z","msg":"咁黑人係咪唔會失眠?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de408695e4584ababd4db72dafff99e8dd2e212e","tid":517322,"uid":150209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"279cb8de4b2f0bac47d291289ea45339e8b4b762","tid":517322,"uid":55724,"like":19,"dislike":5,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"想問好耐，咁我去左外國，然後其實我係香港既6am訓咪會好唔健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:38:27.000Z","msg":"呢個我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似之前去左歐洲咁差5個鐘，<br />\n個邊10點已經香港零晨3點<br />\n咁樣又點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食飯又係，食夜好似變左食消夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9bfba5e781165a0365d08b6ae0fe821c14507bd","tid":517322,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adcc21c031b7b031f1443b1234ff55b144d41030","tid":517322,"uid":106745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>時間根本唔存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>Sorry 更準確日照光強度</blockquote>好似合理，咁一d 日照時間短既地方呢？</blockquote>住極地可以成個冬天都無陽光同埋成個夏天都無夜晚<br />\n所以佢地會有相應嘅問題 e.g. midwinter insomia 同 winter depression (seasonal affective disorder), 而其中一個解決方法就係去照燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">求其google 嘅source <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3793275/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3793275%2F&d=Ny6BDYClu716bB9o07P%2FrYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e037c024\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3793275/</a></span></blockquote><br />\nching well said<br />\n<br />\nbtw有人講左個有根據嘅解釋無人理<br />\n然後其他人係到鬥鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efe21562895589968102ac84ec9054e5d761b53","tid":517322,"uid":62996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:53:06.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"8df27575d879b10c35986bb961cb94d95454d2cc","tid":517322,"uid":37566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"673be790a274d0ec6462171e15d5e43f046c002f","tid":517322,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:07:23.000Z","msg":"你高或者成咗年夜訓就冇乜所謂，<br />\n矮仔未成年就建議就啲訓喇，<br />\n生長激素剩喺12點你訓咗先會分泌多啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T01:16:50.000Z","msg":"關撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c551b2338e720e3896bffc9c5d1ceae29bddee71","tid":517322,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T01:21:28.000Z","msg":"假設係一般家庭，夜晚係安靜夠黑，朝早係會聽到些微街外嘅聲音而且透光，而家有三組生活作息，每組每日都係訓八個鐘，而且進食時間係根據各組作出調整且規律，其他環境因素不變，5am日出，6pm日落：<br />\n<br />\nA. 10pm &mdash; 6am<br />\nB. 6am &mdash; 2pm<br />\nC. 4pm &mdash; 12am<br />\n<br />\n用返上面講過嘅褪黑色素嘅理論，係咪可以講<br />\nA（約7個鐘夜晚）比<br />\nC（約6個鐘夜晚）比<br />\nB（全朝早）<br />\n作息更好？"},{"pid":"551ad77b1622b3f8174abc98926a4097812f22c5","tid":517322,"uid":31048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80f408bf95e141b8bebefe691e489a3dc129d8a3","tid":517322,"uid":28181,"like":7,"dislike":27,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"8ce7f89688ae9481c39c0287ebc87274dd20a297","tid":517322,"uid":133865,"like":173,"dislike":2,"score":171,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T07:52:57.000Z","msg":"黑夜會產生退黑色素，會增加睡眠質素<br />\n當然如果你可以喺朝早制造到一個同夜晚一樣黑既環境，就應該冇問題"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T17:43:12.000Z","msg":"咁黑人係咪唔會失眠?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T01:22:03.000Z","msg":"望住自己就想訓"},{"pid":"6e4b2d3af9e1cbca08d84daa01fa05193d73572f","tid":517322,"uid":59252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ef431ecd8475b4c1feb23c1b8b06eab9e846c57","tid":517322,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"103187f391e46f9ea3b19a974358523cef1590f1","tid":517322,"uid":59252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c96e1d8bdfc0ffb2a58cf0e9fa100e0577a35e6","tid":517322,"uid":55724,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T08:09:17.000Z","msg":"可能我講野唔係太清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我意思係，如果我一樣訓8個鍾既話，<br />\n12訓到8,<br />\n如4訓到12 點解唔可以夜訓，<br />\n而另一個問題就係如果我同樣訓咁多時間，咁係咪其實都無問題（時差）<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T21:04:30.000Z","msg":"啲醫生話最好訓夠八個鐘 對身體好<br />\n但對身體黎講 睡眠時間唔係唯一因素<br />\n<br />\n當你11pm訓7am起身 8個鐘<br />\n6點鐘日出 即係11pm-6am之間係夜晚<br />\n11pm-6am身體就會產生褪黑素<br />\n<br />\n咁又例如你3am先訓 11am先起身 都係8個鐘<br />\n一樣6點鐘日出 咁得3am-6am係夜晚<br />\n變相你身體就短左時間去產生褪黑素<br />\n<br />\n褪黑素令人有更好既睡眠質素<br />\n人通常過左一半既睡眠時間先去到深層睡眠<br />\n用返以上例子 3am-11am<br />\n即係7am-11am係深層睡眠 但6am已經日出<br />\n深層睡眠缺乏褪黑素既幫助會變得唔穩定<br />\n你或者唔會醒 但呢種深層睡眠比夜間既深層睡眠對舒解疲勞方面會無咁好既功效<br />\n<br />\n如果你久而久之 一直都夜訓<br />\n褪黑素對你身體既生理時鐘就會少左影響<br />\n即係你變返早睡早起都係會訓得唔好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T21:13:04.000Z","msg":"咁如果日出之後間房都勁暗係咪就無影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T01:28:56.000Z","msg":"如果你本身係夜訓既人 裝窗簾真係好有用<br />\n我親身經驗真係會好訓啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efe98daa2fba252e1f3d16ac78f900e3434d8ae","tid":517322,"uid":59252,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de408695e4584ababd4db72dafff99e8dd2e212e","tid":517322,"uid":150209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"279cb8de4b2f0bac47d291289ea45339e8b4b762","tid":517322,"uid":55724,"like":19,"dislike":5,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"想問好耐，咁我去左外國，然後其實我係香港既6am訓咪會好唔健康<img src