/PMC3793275/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3793275%2F&d=Ny6BDYClu716bB9o07P%2FrYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e037c024\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3793275/</a></span></blockquote><br />\nching well said<br />\n<br />\nbtw有人講左個有根據嘅解釋無人理<br />\n然後其他人係到鬥鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T02:29:56.000Z","msg":"thanks ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有好多comment 都啱嘅，只係無俾source 啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登有學術討論我已經好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cbbe00e74755d50a8631d5449f427460f319176","tid":517322,"uid":86673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T02:54:54.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"83389069eb099a5ab489bf312b90523a2f96c664","tid":517322,"uid":84367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T02:55:59.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"45f7e1178007445af1d60cfafe4560eb971edb79","tid":517322,"uid":20828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:06:29.000Z","msg":"無話唔可以 香港人全球最長壽<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75bcb8f3d7d6ab166256b028bff726492b059c0","tid":517322,"uid":55724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"103187f391e46f9ea3b19a974358523cef1590f1","tid":517322,"uid":59252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c96e1d8bdfc0ffb2a58cf0e9fa100e0577a35e6","tid":517322,"uid":55724,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"911cad8f5455213d2ab239cb833c92a59e72ad48","tid":517322,"uid":43509,"like":1,"dislike":145,"score":-144,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T07:56:41.000Z","msg":"假設你每日7點起身<br />\n2點訓7點起身<br />\n11點訓7點起身<br />\n你話有無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T08:09:17.000Z","msg":"可能我講野唔係太清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我意思係，如果我一樣訓8個鍾既話，<br />\n12訓到8,<br />\n如4訓到12 點解唔可以夜訓，<br />\n而另一個問題就係如果我同樣訓咁多時間，咁係咪其實都無問題（時差）<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T21:04:30.000Z","msg":"啲醫生話最好訓夠八個鐘 對身體好<br />\n但對身體黎講 睡眠時間唔係唯一因素<br />\n<br />\n當你11pm訓7am起身 8個鐘<br />\n6點鐘日出 即係11pm-6am之間係夜晚<br />\n11pm-6am身體就會產生褪黑素<br />\n<br />\n咁又例如你3am先訓 11am先起身 都係8個鐘<br />\n一樣6點鐘日出 咁得3am-6am係夜晚<br />\n變相你身體就短左時間去產生褪黑素<br />\n<br />\n褪黑素令人有更好既睡眠質素<br />\n人通常過左一半既睡眠時間先去到深層睡眠<br />\n用返以上例子 3am-11am<br />\n即係7am-11am係深層睡眠 但6am已經日出<br />\n深層睡眠缺乏褪黑素既幫助會變得唔穩定<br />\n你或者唔會醒 但呢種深層睡眠比夜間既深層睡眠對舒解疲勞方面會無咁好既功效<br />\n<br />\n如果你久而久之 一直都夜訓<br />\n褪黑素對你身體既生理時鐘就會少左影響<br />\n即係你變返早睡早起都係會訓得唔好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:13:08.000Z","msg":"咁係日照時間短既地方（即係多d夜晚時間） 係唔係會訓得好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且唔怕夜訓？"},{"pid":"10c23323adbf0859b57b0f2bd04d3a91902088d6","tid":517322,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0efe98daa2fba252e1f3d16ac78f900e3434d8ae","tid":517322,"uid":59252,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de408695e4584ababd4db72dafff99e8dd2e212e","tid":517322,"uid":150209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"279cb8de4b2f0bac47d291289ea45339e8b4b762","tid":517322,"uid":55724,"like":19,"dislike":5,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"想問好耐，咁我去左外國，然後其實我係香港既6am訓咪會好唔健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:38:27.000Z","msg":"呢個我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似之前去左歐洲咁差5個鐘，<br />\n個邊10點已經香港零晨3點<br />\n咁樣又點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食飯又係，食夜好似變左食消夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T01:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我反而唔明<br />\n去外地跟返外地時間作息咪得<br />\n睇住個香港時間做乜<br />\n我去親旅行都無時差問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:14:59.000Z","msg":"其實咪講左關日照時間事<br />\n死都要講去外地旅行跟香港時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}